snippet.title: Duels Kings - Official game trailer | English
snippet.description:
Join us on Discord: https://discord.com/invite/TUQV9g6buV
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/duels_kings
Follow us on Instagram: @duels_kings
Download Duels Kings game FREE for Android - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bbcompany.brawlbattle

#DuelsKings #DuelsKingsGame

Duels Kings is a dynamic platformer fighting game.

Take part in epic battles, test amazing heroes, choose the strongest one.  Enter the competitive mode, where the battle for the individual rating awaits you.  Raise your place on the leaderboard and get ready to fight for the title of the best player of the season!  Or join forces with friends, develop tactics and win together.

A more detailed description can be found below.

LOTS OF GAME MODES
 • Quick game
 • Rating 1 v 1
 • Rating 2 v 2
 • Team per team (up to 5 players per team)
 • Champion's Cup
 • Custom tournaments
 • Every man for himself

RATED BATTLES
 • Rating system from Bronze to Legend
 • Leaderboard

CHARACTERS
 • 6 unique heroes in gameplay
 • Stable updates
 • Pumping system for game currency BB
 • Customization / skins

MUSIC KITS
 • 9 music packs
